#### L-6: `RouteContext.Provider` Wrapped Inline in Route Definitions

**What:** [routes/index.jsx](file:///d:/Mallakhamb-Repo/Mallakhamb-server-refactor/Web/src/routes/index.jsx#L113-L115) wraps every admin/superadmin route with `<RouteContext.Provider value={{...}}>`. This is repeated 8 times.

